The mention of computer vision suggests that it may also belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) sub-category. The paper also discusses efficient solutions to the problem, which suggests that it may belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category. The mention of databases suggests that it may also belong to the cs.DB (Databases) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions connections to questions in geometric functional analysis and combinatorial geometry, which suggests that it may also belong to the cs.CG (Computational Geometry) sub-category.
